cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.DC, cs.SY 

The paper deals with the application of multi-party computation (MPC) to fall detection systems, which is a topic related to security and privacy (cs.CR). The use of machine learning-based classification and derivative-based features also suggests a connection to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG). The implementation and evaluation of the system in a cloud-based setting may also relate to the sub-category of cloud computing (cs.CY). The use of inertial measurement units (IMUs) and the exploration of derivative-based features may also suggest a connection to the sub-category of data compression (cs.DC). Finally, the overall system design and evaluation may also relate to the sub-category of systems and control (cs.SY).
